Class Country

java.lang.Object
am.aua.StrategyGame.core.Country
public class Country extends Object
Represents a country in the strategy game. A country has a name, health points (HP), gold, an army of troops, and an upgradeable economy.

  • Constructor Summary

    Constructors

    Country(String name)
